### Activities definitions
# Getting sight
DecisionRule activate_getting_sight {
  X
  { (getting_sight X)! (INFEASIBLE getting_sight X)! (location X) }
  { (getting_sight X)=1.0 (in_sight X) komoGetSight(X)=1. }
}

# that directly terminates!!
Rule {
  X
  { (getting_sight X) }
  { (Terminate getting_sight X) (getting_sight X)! }
}

# Observing
DecisionRule activate_observing {
  X, Y
  { (observing X Y)! (INFEASIBLE observing X Y)! (object X) (location Y) (in_sight Y)}
  { (observing X Y)=1.0 (observed X Y) komoObserve(X Y)=1. }
}

# that directly terminates!!
Rule {
  X, Y
  { (observing X Y) }
  { (Terminate observing X Y) (observing X Y)! (in_sight Y)!}
}

